This Sunday, the top four Idols South Africa season 12 contestants will jet off to the city of dreams, New York, for a week-long working holiday.It remains to be seen who of the remaining top-five contestants will forfeit his/her coveted trip as there s only room for four.The five remaining singing hopefuls are Thami Shobede, Noma Khumalo, Lucia Jakeni, Tebogo Louw and Terra Cox.Nontokozo Gxumisa | news@thenewage.co.za